>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">To date, ZJU or sometimes called Zheda, has become a reputable comprehensive research university placing 35<sup>th</sup> in the Asian rankings and 8<sup>th</sup>, in China&rsquo;s <a href=\"http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings-articles/brics-rankings/top-10-universities-china-2015\" target=\"_blank\">Top Universities 2015/16</a> and 5<sup>th </sup>in the Asian rankings.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">On top of that, Zhejiang University now has 7 faculties and 36 colleges/schools. Click <strong><a href=\"http://bksy.zju.edu.cn/english/redir.php?catalog_id=700004\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></strong> to find out more about the various disciplines within the various schools.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">School&rsquo;s main website: <a href=\"http://www.zju.edu.cn/english/\" target=\"_blank\">English</a> | <a href=\"http://www.zju.edu.cn/\" target=\"_blank\">Mandarin</a></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">International Students website: <a href=\"http://iczu.zju.edu.cn/english/\" target=\"_blank\">English&nbsp;</a>| <a href=\"http://www.eeci-institute.eu/EECI-docs2/GUIDE-Hangzhou%20-%20useful%20information.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">International student&rsquo;s guide</a></span></strong></p>\r\n','<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#FF8C00\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>GPA requirement:</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:293px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Courses</span></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:283px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Grade Requirements</span></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:293px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Visiting / Exchange students:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Liberal arts,</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Science, Engineering, agriculture, economics, business and medical programmes</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Chinese Language Program</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"http://iczu.zju.edu.cn/english/redir.php?catalog_id=230\" target=\"_blank\">Webpage here</a></span></li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:283px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">General visiting students should have college or university studies of at least 2 years.</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">In addition, liberal arts programme applicants should have a minimum of level 6 or above for HSK test score. Applicants of other programs should have an HSK test score of level 4 or above.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:293px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">International Students:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Liberal arts, history, education and law</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Science, Engineering, agriculture, economics, business and medical programmes</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Chinese Language Program</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"http://iczu.zju.edu.cn/english/redir.php?catalog_id=226\" target=\"_blank\">Webpage here</a></span></li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:283px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:8.75pt; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14p