of Engineering. On top of that, they have an inter-library loan service in-collaboration with Pohang University of Science and Technology.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">More information on Hanyang&rsquo;s Industrial Science Library can be found <strong><a href=\"http://www.hanyang.ac.kr/user/indexFrame.action?framePath=div3_1.jsp&amp;siteId=hanyangeng&amp;leftPage=&amp;rightPage=06_04_06.html&amp;codyMenuSeq=1266\">here</a>!</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Phone : +82-2-2290-1378<br />\r\nLocation: 4<sup>th</sup> Floor of Engineering Center</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>PaikNam Academic Information Center &amp; Library </strong><br />\r\nThis library has a total of 9 floors (including 3 basement levels). Various rooms are available for different purposes such as revision, exhibitions, used books, conferences reading and much more.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:132px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Monday to Friday</strong></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:387px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">9:00 a.m. to 9:00 p.m.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:132px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Saturdays</span></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:387px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">9:00 a.m. until 12:00 p.m.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:132px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Website </strong></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:387px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">library.hanyang.ac.kr</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"height:4px; width:132px\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>How to get there</strong></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:4px; width:387px\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Subway Line: Green Subway, Line 2<br />\r\n			Station: &nbsp;Hanyang University<br />\r\n			Exit: Exit No. 2 with stairs leading up to the campus.<br />\r\n			Follow the pathway that leads to the back of the Administration Building and make a left.<br />\r\n			Then make your way up to the top of the hill and you will see the library on the right.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">On top of that, a collection of electronic thesis and dissertations are available for downloads and prints (in full text) anywhere in campus due to existing alliances with the Hanyang University Graduate Schools.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">More information can be found <strong><a href=\"http://www.hanyang.ac.kr/user/indexFrame.action?framePath=div3_1.jsp&amp;siteId=hanyangeng&amp;leftPage=&amp;rightPage=06_04_05.html&amp;codyMenuSeq=1265\">here</a>!</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Stadiums and Tennis Courts</strong> are also available for students within the University compound!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#FF8C00\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Food on campus:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Eateries within and outside Hanyang University are aplenty and may be tough for Hanyangians to decide what to eat! Cafes are normally places that serves the best food but canteens (or dining halls) are generally che